As I have said, I have tried to make the levels play different every time.
The game actually responds to how you play and how you time your assaults!
You may notice sometimes you think you'll be overwhelmed and the next
time you play (using the same skill level) the enemy will probably assault
you in a different way! On some levels you may even notice that your kill
level percentage even exceeds 100%. You may shoot ghosts to get some easy
points and they come back again just to get shot again and again- this adds
to your kill ratio BUT burns up your ammo too!

